Exlusion regions from star catalogue
 BRIGHTSTARCATALOGUE <catalogue file name>
 (catalogues are located in 
  $VERITAS_EVNDISP_AUX_DIR/AstroData/Catalogues/ )
* BRIGHTSTARCATALOGUE Hipparcos_MAG8_1997.dat
Minimum brightness of stars to be added to the list of exclusion regions and
radius of region to be excluded from background calculation around bright star (<=0 to switch off)
 BRIGHTSTARSETTINGS <min magnitude> <radius of exlusion region [deg]> <band (B or V)>
* BRIGHTSTARSETTINGS 6 0.30 B

Sky maps
--------

binning and size
(sky maps are in equatorial coordinates)

binning of sky map (correlated plots) [deg]
* SKYMAPBINSIZE 0.01
binning of sky map (uncorrelated plots) [deg]
* SKYMAPBINSIZEUC 0.05
size of sky map (x-axis/declination axis) [deg]
* SKYMAPSIZEX 2.
size of sky map (y-axis/RA axis) [deg]
* SKYMAPSIZEY 2.

sky map centre
(default: target coordinates)
in equatorial coordinates (ra,dec) (J2000, deg)
