(default is at sky map centre)

relative to (0,0) in sky map [deg]
(West,North)
 TARGETXYSHIFT 0. 0.
Position in equatorial coordinates (ra,dec) (J2000, deg)
 TARGETPOSITION_RADECJ2000_DEG 83.633114 22.014487
Position in equatorial coordinates (ra,dec) (J2000, hours)
 TARGETPOSITION_RADECJ2000_HOUR 05 34 31.95 +22 00 52.2

Spectral reconstruction
-----------------------

Spectral index for effective areas
(should be iteratively adjusted to match the measured
spectrum)
 ENERGYSPECTRALINDEX <spectral index>
* ENERGYSPECTRALINDEX 2.4

Energy spectra binning (logarithmic axis)
* ENERGYBINSIZE 0.05
Dead time calculation
(0=using L1 scalars (default), 
 1=using tdiff distributions (not as accurate as L1 scalar method))
* DEADTIMECALCULATIONMETHOD 0

